!!!Work in progress
The tests are usage examples for now and don't do proper assertions yet.
-----------------------------------

A Beanstalk client in utilising node.js.
Depends on the yaml package in kiwi.

For simple usage examples check the test folder.

It is a bit counter intuitive when one has to close the 
socket via .disconnect() in order to be able to go through 
the tube contents by calling reserve()

Also included is the cli demo app 'beanspector', that just outputs
info about tubes and gives one the possibility to empty it.


